      • getFilenames

        public static List<String> getFilenames(File dir)
        Returns the filenaes of the testfiles depending on the type of the testfile. The filename of a file with contains a broken query (a query which the parser do not acceapt) must start with "BDPL-BrokenQuery". The filename of a file with a regular query must start with "BDPL-Query".
        Parameters:
        dir - Directory of the files.
        type - Type of the fiel.
        Returns:
        All filenames with the specified type.
